# Aegis StadiumOS / PitchControl
# Example Environment Variables

# The AI Orchestration engine uses Gemini 2.5
# Get your key from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# If this is left blank, PitchControl will automatically use a local mock fallback.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GEMINI_API_KEY="your_api_key_here"
